## Summary of Key Patterns

| Pattern | Location | Purpose |
|---------|----------|---------|
| **Drag Handle** | Icon span with `{...listeners}` | Enables dragging |
| **Click Disable** | State + useRef timeout | Prevents navigation during drag |
| **Order Persistence** | useSidebarNavStore | Saves drag order to IndexedDB |
| **Folder Nesting** | parentId field + validation | Unlimited hierarchy with cycle prevention |
| **Hover Actions** | `opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100` | Progressive disclosure without layout shift |
| **Dropdown** | useRef + click-outside listener | Position and dismiss behavior |

All of these patterns work together to create a smooth, accessible drag-and-drop experience without fighting with React routing!
